        "raw": "Question: Someone Who Influenced You\nDescribe someone who has had an important influence on your life.\n（題目：一位對你人生有重要影響的人）\nYou should say:\n（你應該說明：）\n● Who the person is\n（那個人是誰）\n● How long you have known him/her\n（你認識他／她多久了）\n● What qualities this person has\n（這個人有甚麼特質）\n● Explain why they have had such an influence on you\n（解釋為甚麼他／她對你有這麼大的影響）\nPPF idea for this topic\nKeep one main person throughout the whole answer.\nTalk about when this person entered your life and what they did in the past,\nhow their influence is still affecting you now, and how it may shape your future.\n（PPF 小提示：全程集中講同一個人。先講這個人在過去如何走進你的生命、\n做過甚麼；再講這份影響現在如何仍然存在；最後講它將來可能怎樣影響\n你。）"
