        "raw": "Question: An Interesting Person\nDescribe a person that you think is very interesting.\n（題目：一個你覺得很有趣的人）\nYou should say:\nWho is this person\n（這個人是誰）\nHow you met them\n（你如何認識他／她）\nWhat they like to talk about\n（他／她喜歡談甚麼）\nExplain why this person is very interesting.\n（解釋為甚麼你覺得這個人很有趣）\nPPF idea: keep one main person, talk about how you met them in the past, what\nthey are like now, and how they may influence you in the future.\n（PPF 小提示：集中說同一個人物，先講你過去如何認識他，再講他現在是怎\n樣的人，以及他將來可能怎樣影響你。）"
