        "raw": "Question: Describe your favourite teacher from school.\n(題目：描述你在學校最喜歡的一位老師。)\nYou should say:\n(你應該說明：)\nWhat school he/she taught at\n(他／她在哪一間學校任教)\nWhat he/she looked like\n(他／她長甚麼樣子)\nWhat subject he/she taught you\n(他／她教你甚麼科目)\nExplain why you remember this teacher so well.\n(解釋你為甚麼對這位老師印象這麼深刻。)\nPPF idea: Past — when this teacher taught you and what classes were like;\nPresent — why you still remember this teacher now; Future — what lessons\nfrom this teacher may stay with you in the future.\n(PPF 小提示：可以用過去、現在、未來去延伸同一位老師，例如他以前怎樣教\n你、你現在為何仍然記得他，以及他帶給你的影響將來如何延續下去。)"
