          "headingZh": "(1. 開場：這位老師是誰，以及他在哪間學校任教（過去）)",
          "textEn": "My favourite teacher from school was my secondary school history teacher, Mr Chan. He taught at the government secondary school I attended from Form One to Form Six, and he taught me for about two years. I first met him when I was in junior secondary school, and even now I can still remember the atmosphere in his classroom very clearly.",
          "textZh": "(我在學校最喜歡的一位老師，是我中學時期的歷史老師陳老師。他在我由中一讀到中六的那間官立中學任教，而他大概教了我兩年。我第一次認識他是在初中時期，直到現在，我仍然很清楚記得他課堂上的那種氣氛。)"
