        "raw": "Describe your favourite childhood friend.\n(描述你最喜歡的一位童年朋友。)\n● You should say:\n(你應該說明：)\n● who he/she is\n(他／她是誰)\n● where you met each other\n(你們在哪裡認識)\n● what you often did together\n(你們經常一起做甚麼)\n● and explain what made you like him/her\n(並解釋為甚麼你喜歡他／她)\nPPF idea: keep one main friend as the focus, talk about how you met in the past,\nwhat you used to do together, how you feel about the friendship now, and what\nyou hope for in future.\n(PPF 小提示：集中講同一位朋友，先講你們過去如何認識、以前常常一起做\n甚麼，再講你現在怎樣看這段友情，以及你對未來有甚麼想法。)"
